"title": "4805: clouds",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4805: clouds",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A natural feature of the sky, often associated with God's judgment, presence and glory.</p>\n<h2>Clouds as a natural phenomenon</h2>\n<h3>Rain clouds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:44-1Kgs18:45\">1KI 18:44–18:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:13-Gen9:16\">GEN 9:13–9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:28\">JOB 36:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:3\">ECC 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:54\">LUK 12:54</a></p>\n<h3>Clouds representing the sky</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:6\">JOB 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job35:5\">JOB 35:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:14\">ISA 14:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:9\">JER 51:9</a></p>\n<h3>Clouds subject to God's sovereign control</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:13\">JOB 37:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:4\">JDG 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:8\">JOB 26:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:7\">PSA 135:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8\">PSA 147:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:20\">PRO 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:28\">PRO 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:6\">ISA 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:13\">JER 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:16\">JER 51:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:1\">ZEC 10:1</a></p>\n<h3>Clouds expressing the mystery of God's world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:15-Job37:16\">JOB 37:15–37:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:14\">JOB 22:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:9\">JOB 26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:29\">JOB 36:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:9\">JOB 38:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:37\">JOB 38:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:4\">ECC 11:4</a></p>\n<h3>Clouds of smoke</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:13\">LEV 16:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:38\">JDG 20:38</a></p>\n<h2>Clouds as symbols of spiritual truths</h2>\n<h3>A symbol of judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:3\">EZK 30:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:18\">EZK 30:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:12\">EZK 34:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:2\">JOL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:15\">ZEP 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of blessing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:8\">ISA 45:8</a></p>\n<h3>A symbol of impermanence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:9\">JOB 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:15\">JOB 30:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:15\">PRO 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:4\">HOS 6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:3\">HOS 13:3</a></p>\n<h3>Other positive symbolic uses</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:5\">ISA 25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:22\">ISA 44:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a></p>\n<h3>Other negative symbolic uses</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:14\">PRO 25:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:2\">ECC 12:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:12\">JUD 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>Clouds as a symbol of God's presence and glory</h2>\n<h3>Revealing God's majesty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:3\">NAM 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:11\">JOB 37:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:2\">PSA 97:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:27\">ISA 30:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:30\">ISA 30:30</a>DEU <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:26\">33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:4\">PSA 68:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:3\">PSA 104:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:13\">JER 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>The cloud of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21-Exod13:22\">EXO 13:21–13:22</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:15-Num9:22\">NUM 9:15–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:11-Num10:12\">NUM 10:11–10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:34\">NUM 10:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:25\">NUM 11:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:14\">NUM 14:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:15\">DEU 31:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:12\">NEH 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:19\">NEH 9:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:14\">PSA 78:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:7\">PSA 99:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:39\">PSA 105:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:19-Exod14:20\">EXO 14:19–14:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:24\">EXO 14:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:1-1Cor10:2\">1CO 10:1–10:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">REV 14:14</a></p>\n<h3>The cloud of God's awesomeness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:2\">LEV 16:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:9\">EXO 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:16\">EXO 19:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:5\">EXO 34:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:5\">NUM 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:10\">NUM 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:11\">DEU 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:22\">DEU 5:22</a></p>\n<h3>The cloud of God's glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:10-1Kgs8:12\">1KI 8:10–8:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13-2Chr6:1\">2CH 5:13–6:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:10\">EXO 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:15-Exod24:18\">EXO 24:15–24:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:9-Exod33:10\">EXO 33:9–33:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:34-Exod40:38\">EXO 40:34–40:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:42\">NUM 16:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:28\">EZK 1:28</a></p>\n<h2>Clouds revealing Jesus Christ's glory</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:34\">LUK 9:34</a> <em>Jesus Christ's transfiguration</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:9\">ACT 1:9</a></strong> <em>Jesus Christ's ascension</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:7\">REV 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13\">DAN 7:13</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan24:30\">24:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">MRK 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:27\">LUK 21:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:64\">MAT 26:64</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:62\">MRK 14:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:17</a></p>",
